---
title: Chicken & Poblano Fajitas with Pico de Gallo, Monterey Jack & Smoky Red Pepper Crema
description: Tonight’s meal is quick, easy, and downright delicious. It’s got it all—we’re talking spiced chicken, strips of poblano, and sliced onion, all tossed on a baking sheet and roasted until tender and lightly charred. The joyous jumble is then piled into steamy flour tortillas along with fresh salsa, a drizzle of smoky red pepper crema, and a sprinkle of Monterey Jack cheese. Talk about a fiesta on your plate!

Put the world on your plate with this curated collection of internationally inspired meals to satisfy your wanderlust.
